- Women's Trade Union League Report, 1909</stimulus>
        <prompt>This excerpt best illustrates which challenge to Progressive Era reform?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Language and cultural barriers</option>
            <option letter="b">Government corruption</option>
            <option letter="c">Corporate resistance</option>
            <option letter="d">Religious differences</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The report highlights how language and cultural barriers among immigrant workers complicated labor organizing efforts, a significant challenge to Progressive reforms.</explanation>
